# Pinch Project Rules

- Use JSDoc syntax for all public-facing method doc blocks.
- Architecture: Enforce the Facade pattern. Components talk to Facades, never Infrastructure services.
- Types: Strict typing is mandatory. No 'any'. Explicit return types on all functions.
- RxJS: Use the async pipe in templates to manage subscriptions.
- State: All async actions must trigger updates to the relevant `status$` observable.